\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oju1665703215261.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oju1665703215261.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oju1665703215261.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oju1665703215261\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether the UHTTP component uses registry settings on Microsoft Windows systems.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"oju1665703215261__topic_d138617e1_d138618e1_d138619e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oju1665703215261__p_d138620e1_d138621e1_d138622e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oju1665703215261__section_xsj_ltt_yvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549953e68\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"oju1665703215261__table_d16448e1_d16449e1_d16450e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> application files </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzg1665702547028.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzg1665702547028.html\" title=\"Use the [PROXY_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to configure a proxy server for use by the UHTTP component.\">[PROXY_SETTINGS]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Values </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> —use Registry settings if $SERVER and $BYPASS are omitted </p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>—do not use Registry settings</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> none </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oju1665703215261__section_itf_rtt_yvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549953e142\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oju1665703215261__p_d138629e1_d138630e1_d138631e1\">By default, on Microsoft Windows, the UHTTP component\n        uses the registry settings to determine the proxy server and the servers that can be\n        accessed directly, bypassing the proxy server. You can override the registry settings using\n        the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SERVER</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$BYPASS</span> assignment settings.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oju1665703215261__p_d138632e1_d138633e1_d138634e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY</span> to\n        determine whether the UHTTP component uses registry settings on Microsoft Windows systems if\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SERVER</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$BYPASS</span> are omitted.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oju1665703215261__section_vsb_vvt_yvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549953e169\">Example: $DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"oju1665703215261__pre_nym_wvt_yvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[PROXY_SETTINGS]\n$DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY = 1</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wnk1665702545934.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UHTTP</a><p>The Uniface UHTTP component is an HTTP client that is used for sending and receiving HTTP requests and responses. It provides operations for executing HTTP requests used for web applications and RESTful web services.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/npm1665703214870.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$BYPASS</a><p>Set the host identifiers or IP addresses to which the UHTTP component should connect directly,and not through a proxy server.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ztt1665703215559.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$SERVER</a><p>Set the proxy server to be used by the UHTTP component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530612\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530612\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify whether the UHTTP component uses registry settings on Microsoft Windows systems. $DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY { = } 0 | 1 Defaults Assignment file: application files Section: [PROXY_SETTINGS] Values 0 —use Registry settings if $SERVER and $BYPASS are omitted 1 —do not use Registry settings Default value: none Description By default, on Microsoft Windows, the UHTTP component uses the registry settings to determine the proxy server and the servers that can be accessed directly, bypassing the proxy server. You can override the registry settings using the $SERVER and $BYPASS assignment settings. You can use $DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY to determine whether the UHTTP component uses registry settings on Microsoft Windows systems if $SERVER and $BYPASS are omitted. Example: $DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY [PROXY_SETTINGS] $DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY = 1 Copy Related Links UHTTP The Uniface UHTTP component is an HTTP client that is used for sending and receiving HTTP requests and responses. It provides operations for executing HTTP requests used for web applications and RESTful web services. $BYPASS Set the host identifiers or IP addresses to which the UHTTP component should connect directly,and not through a proxy server. $SERVER Set the proxy server to be used by the UHTTP component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}